HEADWORD: Milt
<hw>Milt</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS. <ets>milte</ets>;
akin to D. <ets>milt</ets>, G. <ets>milz</ets>, OHG. <ets>milzi</ets>,
